# Database

# For local development:
# DATABASE_URL="file:./db/custom.db"

# For Vercel serverless (uses /tmp which is writable but ephemeral):
# The db.ts file automatically handles this — no need to set DATABASE_URL
# The empty template at db/teamhub-empty.db is copied to /tmp/teamhub.db
# on each cold start.

# IMPORTANT LIMITATION:
# On Vercel serverless, each function invocation may hit a different container.
# SQLite data in /tmp does NOT persist across containers.
# This means: data may "disappear" between requests on cold instances.
#
# For production use, please use Vercel Postgres or another persistent DB:
# https://vercel.com/docs/storage/vercel-postgres
